data.description: Great Home in a quite location setting on a generous 1.685 acres with endless outdoor possibilities. The home is featured with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a loft ceiling, in the living room, wood burning fireplace, split bedroom plan, master suite with a generously sized walk-in closet and laundry room. The home also comes with an outdoor storage shed. Roof is in Great Conditions. Home is also in a preferred flood zone X. It is a great home for first time home owner or family that loves spacious outdoors and don't mind doing a little TLC. Property is part of a succession and needs to go fast! Buyer may possibly be able to assume the current VA Loan on the property, but an assumption is subject to finance company approval.
